</div>

{{!-- SECTION DEMO: Define sidebar content specific to home page --}}
{{#section "sidebar"}}
  <div class="sidebar" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h3>ðŸ“Œ About Sections</h3>
    <p><strong>Sections</strong> allow child templates to inject content into specific areas of the layout.</p>
    <ul>
      <li><code>&#123;&#123;&#123;body&#125;&#125;&#125;</code> - Main content section (built-in)</li>
      <li><code>&#123;&#123;&#123;_sections.styles&#125;&#125;&#125;</code> - Custom CSS section</li>
      <li><code>&#123;&#123;&#123;_sections.sidebar&#125;&#125;&#125;</code> - This sidebar section</li>
    </ul>
    <p><em>This sidebar was defined using <code>&#123;&#123;#section "sidebar"&#125;&#125;</code> in home.handlebars</em></p>
  </div>
{{/section}}
